nodes.text: A female pilot from Corellia, born in the town of Doaba Guerfel, took a mission for the Resistance to steal an encryption key from the First Order. She acquired the key and escaped in a stolen TIE fighter, but was pursued. The pilot unsuccessfully attempted to contact the Resistance, before choosing to send the encryption key to a friend from the Collective, who she had formerly worked for. The pilot was killed, but managed to send the key before her fighter was destroyed.
